title: KPop Demon Hunters Zoey Youtooz Vinyl Figure
body_html:
Watch out, demons, Zoey's here to seal you away with her Youtooz debut!

Standing at 4.5 inches tall and holding a trio of purple-tipped shin-kals in each hand as a confident smirk crossed her face, short black hair runs along her forehead in a blunt fringe as long strands fall down either side of heart-marked cheeks, and the bulk is pulled into 2 tight braided buns at the back of her head. Dressed in a long-sleeved white top with golden detailing across the chest and shoulders that matches her short skirt and belt, light purple and blue patterns run along each sleeve as she wears calf-high laced platform boots.

The exterior of her packaging features glowing shimmery effects amidst hazy pink and blue hues, while the interior is filled with a deep blue that's covered in small white dots. The protective sleeve is then a soft blue to purple gradient with thin lines wrapping over its surface, as her figure can be seen through the large, clear window at the packaging's front. This collectible ships in a matte, embossed, protective outer sleeve and a custom-sized plastic protector for maximum protection during shipping.

  • Preorder figure is non-refundable
  • Size: Height: 4.5"
